WF-005 | Edit existing loan product — Save with Accounting_Method != None (reveal GL mappings) | actor: Authenticated user with product configuration permissions | branch: Accounting_Method != None | terminal: Save | on_success: creates or updates loan product template
WF-006 | Cancel out of create/edit wizard (discard changes) | actor: Authenticated user with product configuration permissions | branch: none | terminal: Cancel | on_success: closes wizard without saving
